		<RichText x="738" y="223" width="424" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">水丘丘游侠使用镰刀进行快速的两段攻击，分别造成<span color="#7fbfff">80%,100%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="223" width="422" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">水丘丘游侠使用镰刀进行一段较长时间的蓄力回旋，造成<span color="#7fbfff">100%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="511" width="424" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">距离玩家较远时，水丘丘游侠追逐玩家并给一镰刀，造成<span color="#7fbfff">100%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="799" width="438" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">水丘丘游侠将自身挂水，召唤出<span textDecoration="underline">水史莱姆</span><span>，使其发射3个水泡，触碰造成</span><span color="#7fbfff">50%</span><span>伤害，之后大水史莱姆变小，被水丘丘游侠踢出，造成</span><span color="#7fbfff">100%</span><span>伤害。<br/>用元素反应破除水史莱姆可瘫痪游侠。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="511" width="399" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">距离玩家较近时，水丘丘游侠掰直镰刀，戳击，造成<span color="#7fbfff">80%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="799" width="414" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">水丘丘游侠丢出3个小水史莱姆，造成<span color="#7fbfff">80%,40%,20%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="64" y="501" fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W04" fontSize="40" fontStyle="italic" fontWeight="normal" color="#7fbfff" width="230" height="43" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W04" fontSize="40" fontStyle="italic" color="#7fbfff">永恒异乡人</p>
			</content>
			<filters>
