				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">水史莱姆：<span color="#7fbfff">2水</span><span>盾，受击会为周围挂2单位</span><span color="#7fbfff">水元素</span><span>。</span></p>
